title: The <span style="color: #097100;">**DBP**</span> shifts towards the left
subtitle: Progressivism is beginning to take root among the Rural parties
view-if: dbp_left >= 9 and not dbp_left_seen
on-arrival: dbp_left_seen = 1; dbp_congress_timer = 6;
tags: event

As the DBP shifts further to the left, due to the <span style="color: #c90000;">**SPD**</span> being seen as the only non-rural party helping the peasant class, we have noticed that their left-most factions are growing stronger and stronger. Could the Agrarian parties convert to progressivism